##Banlangen granules are out of stock overseas, but it can not cure new coronary pneumonia

Function introduction, the interface news is China has the influence original financial and economic new media, only serves the independent thinking crowd

Reporter Jin Miao

Editor | Yue Xu

“

Every epidemic, Banlangen will be snapped up.

”

“

Every epidemic, Banlangen will be snapped up.

”

With the global spread of the new crown disease, China's treatment experience has been promoted to the sea. At a press conference held by the Joint Prevention and Control Mechanism of the State Council on March 17, Zhang Xinmin, director of the Biological Center of the Ministry of Science and Technology, said that key drugs such as Fabiravir, convalescent plasma and Chinese medicine had been provided to the countries affected by the outbreak. But did not elaborate on the specific Chinese medicine offered.

Chinese medicine therapy in the new crown treatment, be sought after. On March 10, the National Health Commission and the State Administration of Traditional Chinese Medicine issued the seventh edition of the COVID-19, lianhua Qingwen, Huoxiang Zhengqi, Jinhua Qinggan Granules, Angong Niuhuang pills and other proprietary Chinese medicines continued in the list.

At the same time, overseas demand for Chinese medicines has soared. Demand for Chinese herbal medicines has surged in clinics in New York and San Francisco, and honeysuckle and Banlangen powder have become big sellers, a Chinese Medicine Practitioner said in an interview, prices are rising rapidly.

According to the Shanghai Securities News, two Chinese medicines, Lotus Qingwen of yiling pharmaceutical and Jinhua Qinggan of Juxiechang, have joined Chinese medical experts to aid countries such as Italy and Iraq.

As Chinese medicine to the sea heating up, some investors began to ask listed companies Isatis Tinctoria, honeysuckle and other Chinese medicine exports.

Speaking on the investor relations platform on March 13, China Resources 39 said the company's overseas business was a tiny part of its overall business, with Isatis Tinctoria having a small export business (some of which has recently been used for donations) . With the control of new pneumonia in China, the situation in overseas countries is becoming more and more serious. The company has been studying the opportunities to expand overseas markets.

But in fact, on Jan. 21, the official microblog of the National Health and Human Services Commission, Health China, has refuted the rumor that Isatis Tinctoria was using it to prevent new crown pneumonia, said Dr. Hua Zhang, chief of suction medicine at Hepingli Hospital, isatis Tinctoria is suitable for the treatment of wind-heat colds, viral colds and other hot diseases. It has a certain antiviral effect, but it is unlikely to be effective against coronavirus.

During the SARS outbreak in 2003, Isatis Tinctoria said, Smash, as the concept of an outbreak, was snapped up whenever an outbreak occurred. A total of 1,251 entries were found on the website of the State Drug Administration, which was searched by interface journalists. Medicine Rubik's cube previously reported that in 2017 there were 726 domestic Banlangen granule production enterprises, in addition to Syrup, soft capsules, effervescent tablets, chewable tablets, dispersible tablets and other dosage forms.

However, the raw material of Radix isatidis granules, Radix Isatidis, has always been a serious disaster area. In February 2017, the former State Food and Drug Administration issued the circular no. 21 of 2017 on 54 batches of Chinese herbal pieces that were found to be unqualified, among the 54 batches of substandard Chinese herbal pieces, Isatis Tinctoria failed 28 batches, accounting for more than half.

In March 2018, the State Pharmacopoeia Commission issued the public notice on the proposed revision of the quality standard for Banlangen Granules, which revised the preparation and identification of Banlangen Granules and added the content determination items.

Although the revised standard of Banlangen Granules promotes the quality of Banlangen Granules, it also brings a new round of price increase of Banlangen granules. But the battle for Isatis Tinctoria's efficacy has not been lost since SARS.
